---
title: Sea Bass and Tarragon Sauce with Smashed Potatoes and Sugar Snap Peas
description: This delicious Sea Bass and Tarragon Sauce has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sea-bass-and-tarragon-sauce-bd3d2503-de0e0bf3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/sea-bass-and-tarragon-sauce-629e16d9996748489f0f9f27-cf29ddba.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/sea-bass-and-tarragon-sauce-629e16d9996748489f0f9f27
